Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.84,0:02:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因哈特选手  被击倒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.53,0:02:59.12,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,0)\1cFFFFFF\bord0\pos(1037,615)}损伤模拟  全身扭伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}开始计时  1
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}2
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂罗娜好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是爱因哈特还没拿出真本事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}4
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位选手都做好了准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛继续
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Grand Gazer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人凝视
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空破断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:03:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提奥  借用一下你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霸王流
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破城锤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因哈特选手将魔像击得粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面  珂罗娜选手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出界倒数
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.54,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,0)\1cFFFFFF\bord0\pos(295,481)}珂罗娜·缇米尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}20
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺威  珂罗娜小姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}19
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吵  还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}18
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}17
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量  体力  魔法量——在这些方面她是四人中最平凡的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}16
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}15
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}14
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她能在危机时依然保持冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}13
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}12
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有为了获胜而建立战术的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的智慧和发散思维是四个人中最强的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:04:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那种状态下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还握有武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂罗娜选手  回到擂台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一回合还剩下20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果让她在休息期间得到恢复的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后果无法设想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是珂罗娜同学并不会薇薇欧那样的防守反击以及格斗战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样在近战上压倒她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为圣·希尔德的一年级生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与薇薇欧相遇  成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说她在练习格斗技的时候大吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟她在一起于是与她一起练习
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道我是否真的喜欢格斗技
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:06:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但感觉如果放弃的话就没法跟薇薇欧在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上  我的训练成绩不像薇薇欧那样好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法让自己开心  有好几次想要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个时候诺威师傅总会鼓励我  指导我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说着「最喜欢格斗技了  想要变强」的薇薇欧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远是那么迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边说着「想更加熟练掌握春光拳」一边努力的莉奥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也很帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.86,0:06:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承了先祖的遗志  想得到真正的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命着的爱因哈特是那么出色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成为在那队伍中不拖后腿的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要继续跟大家在同一高度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的速度前进
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂罗娜选手呆立原地  这会带来危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算会疼痛  也要使用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Nephilim Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人之拳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强烈的一击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因哈特选手  动弹不能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}开始计时  1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(681,646)\fs36}Accel Smash
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(890,646)\fs36}Revolver Spike
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那不是薇薇欧的迅疾破碎和回旋钉刺吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}2
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}3
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(488,646)\fs36}Nephilim Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人之拳成功运作起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}4
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在此能决出胜负的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}6
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因哈特选手能站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}7
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}8
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来了  在计时至8的时候
