Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:18.52,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,0)\1cFFFFFF\bord0\pos(1037,689)}损伤模拟  中度脑震荡  视野模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是双方生命值已低至危险区域
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场比赛胜负难料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.94,0:08:22.28,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,0)\1cFFFFFF\bord0\pos(302,101)}珂罗娜·缇米尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为她不会在格斗战中经行反击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.39,0:08:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我低估了珂罗娜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会就这样结束的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩10秒…没有时间创成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Wristlet Form
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护腕形态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(572,646)\fs36}Nephilim Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用巨人之拳打倒她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛继续进行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  珂罗娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候学会那种技术了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了…在这里决出胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:30.89,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,0)\1cFFFFFF\bord0\pos(968,656)}损伤模拟  左臂剧烈扭伤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强烈的打击命中  但是第一回合已经结束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因哈特选手凭借微弱的生命值存活了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂罗娜那招…是我的虎咆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(634,646)\fs36}Nephilim Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然巨人之拳是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:09:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体自动操作？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  以操作魔像的方式来操作自己的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的力量足以操纵巨大的魔像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此进行打击的话  就是名副其实的「巨人之拳」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时她应该是事前编好动作作为触媒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使得反击动作能被自动触发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  只要感应到特定打击就自动作出反击的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就形成了无需反应时间的防守反击呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对策呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才已经想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下个回合试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:43.92,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,0)\1cFFFFFF\bord0\pos(269,479)}爱因哈特·斯崔特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:43.92,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,0)\1cFFFFFF\bord0\pos(269,689)}损伤模拟  全身轻度扭伤  左臂中度扭伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(510,646)\fs36}Nephilim Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人之拳的运转很稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个回合就以格斗战来决出胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:54.14,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,0)\1cFFFFFF\bord0\pos(1003,543)}珂罗娜·缇米尔
Comment: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是珂罗娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有那项技巧  格斗战也能赢对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二回合  开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(593,646)\fs36}Nephilim Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人之拳发动
