Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近距离格斗速攻模式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}System Load
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统读取
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过上步发出猛烈连击  这完全是薇薇欧同学的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Stun Knuckle
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震撼拳击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(745,646)\fs36}Stun Knuckle
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺威小姐的震撼拳击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反击要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.72,0:11:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模式切换  完全防御
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:12:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春光拳的拆招动作  接下来是自动反击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能够预判了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是神速的自动反击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会受到珂罗娜同学自身动作的限制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没法反击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此  连击的速攻也开始失效了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来  身体操作就会出现延迟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从判断到动作的微妙延迟在格斗战中将是致命的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.89,0:12:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  如果是单发的大威力招式  就没这个缺点…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是这样  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(540,646)\fs36}Nephilim Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(734,646)\fs36}Meist Arm
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人之拳  创成巨腕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体的自动操作和坚固的腕部武装
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说这个的对策是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:13:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从六百年前就一直在研究的课题了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:11.45,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,0)\1cFFFFFF\bord0\pos(1000,670)}损伤模拟  右臂扭转挫伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因哈特选手  强烈的一击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  珂罗娜选手仍然坚挺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有进入击倒倒计时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很痛  但应该还能继续
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(576,646)\fs36}Revolver Canon
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(829,646)\fs36}Spike
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先是左手的回旋炮击然后是钉刺的连击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢体之型  牙山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不减弱威力  直接用肘部格挡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是利用对手的攻击力的攻性防御
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:13:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂罗娜选手  用来攻击的部位接连受到冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是爱因哈特选手的追击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳头要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  自动反击还在运作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂罗娜选手倒地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}开始计时  1
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准确预判出自动反击的发动时机  令其打空再加以反击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且当勾拳完全展开后再从上方给予重击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}3
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是完美的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  珂罗娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}4
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的攻性防御让拳和腿都受到了冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}5
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是信心受挫也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}6
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂罗娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(515,646)\fs36}Meist Arts
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(721,646)\fs36}Nephilim Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为创成战技和巨人之拳的精髓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才刚刚开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂罗娜选手站了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会就这么结束
