Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(732,646)\fs36}Full Control Mode
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人之拳  五体完全操作模式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五体的完全操作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是从外部进行驱动的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然感觉就原理跟提线木偶差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样的话也就能自由活动这只手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  这样也没问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:16:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样  其实我很厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂罗娜同学也到达了这一步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Phantom Dive
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵动潜击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被防住了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此  我也要不断尝试  直到打中为止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是骨折  手臂撕裂却仍然坚持战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是五体的完全外部操作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换的是超出极限的动作造成的身体损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生于和平时代的竞技选手不应该使用这样的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手和脚  还有全身都好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的王牌也无法达成决定性一击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论我怎么努力  都赢不了爱因哈特同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  信心受挫了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂罗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂罗娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没有发挥出练习时的全部实力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起练习时的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(617,646)\fs36}Golem Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为魔像创主的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放弃  让我们见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有秘密的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不用这么胡来的打法  珂罗娜小姐依然是很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你奥德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管我也是个格斗技选手  但在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Tact Form
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动形态
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自动操作解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切换到魔法战了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提奥  全力警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Caging Spears
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁锢枪阵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(555,646)\fs36}Brunzell
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  布伦希尔  再一次请求你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Yes anytime
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(806,646)\fs36}Brunzell
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以创主珂罗娜和魔导器布伦希尔之名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复活吧  巨神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(714,646)\fs36}Goliath
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击碎她  歌利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(858,646)\fs36}Goliath
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用破城槌的话  一击就能把歌利亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Maist Arm
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创成巨腕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Spiral Finger
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋指击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习果然还是太辛苦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是很奇怪自己为什么要练到这个程度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这一切都是为了最美妙的瞬间而存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最美妙的瞬间？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过练习  让使出的招式变得利落时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重重地打出会心一击时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切身体会到自己变得比之前更强大时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种瞬间  我希望你们能尽可能多的去体验
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有时也会让你们练习得很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让你也能体会到克服困难后所带来的快乐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Comet Blast
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彗星冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Shoot
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺威师傅教给我的是成长所带来的快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪我特训的奥德对于我的成长由衷地感到高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要展示给他们看的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正能让我感到自豪的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是我一个人冥思苦想出来的必杀技
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.00,0:20:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是整个团队和教练一起为我打造的练习成果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Rock Bind
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚磐束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.45,0:20:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.05,0:20:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提奥  多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(744,646)\fs36}Brunzell
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(911,646)\fs36}Goliath
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这一招决胜负吧  布伦希尔  歌利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:20:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Purge Blast
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射部件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Drill Crusher Punch
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞钻粉碎爆冲拳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.11,0:21:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霸王流  旋冲波
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真正的最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霸王  断空拳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因哈特选手获胜
